extendedInfo.description: Beaumont Dental Associates is here to help, not to judge.  Located in Beaumont, Texas, Beaumont Dental Associates offers all dental services for you and your family.  From root canals to cosmetic dentistry to our brand new snoring and sleep apnea solutions, Beaumont Dental Associates offers the most professional and affordable dental services.  Our dentists Dr. J. Charles Clinkscales, DDS and Dr. Teresa Canzoneri, DDS both bring years of experience, expertise, and a gentle chair side manner to Beaumont Dental Associates. Also, Beaumont Dental Associates offers the latest techniques and technology available in many areas of cosmetic dentistry, including veneers, whitening, crowns, bridges, bonding and implants. Beaumont Dental Associates recognize that each case is unique, and Dr. Clinkscales and Dr. Canzoneri customize your treatment to ensure that all of your needs are met.
